Scanning Daemon
---
* Go through files
* If MP3 scan ID3 data
* UI for easily modifying items (based on folder, etc)


Streaming Server
---
* Realtime transcoding
* Handle multiple streams
* Allow multiple people to stream a single stream
* Dynamic playlist

